race.comment: ZIPPING HILDA (6) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in her brilliant 22.65 win at this track over 401m. Hard to top on the time from two back. BOSTON BANNER (1) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 0.8 lengths (22.95) behind Calla Rusty at this track. Expected to be in this for a long way. SUMMER DREAM (7) below best last time at this track (22.91) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 4.5 lengths fourth. Looks well placed here and among the chances. OPEN ROAD (2) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.
